        <h3>Works with your app</h3>
        <div>
          <p>Transparent HTTP/1.1, HTTP/2, and TCP communication</p>
          <p>No administrator privileges required</p>
          <p>No changes to your existing application code or
            network</p>
        </div>
        <a class="nav" href="{{site_url}}/start/index.html">Try Skupper out <i class="material-icons">chevron_right</i></a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>Security is built in</h3>
        <div>
          <p>Connect services without exposing them to the public
            internet</p>
          <p>All communication is secured by mutual TLS</p>
          <p>Application-level access control and resource limits</p>
          <!-- <p>Supports standard end-to-end authentication between -->
          <!--   clients and servers</p> -->
        </div>
        <a class="nav" href="{{site_url}}/intro/security.html">Skupper security <i class="material-icons">chevron_right</i></a>
